snippet.title: OMORI Console Trailer
snippet.description:
OMORI is coming for Nintendo Switch, PlayStation, and Xbox on June 17th, 2022.

--trailer credits--
director: OMOCAT (www.omocat.com)
music: bo en - my time (omori ver.)
